Package: spacetimegp_tools
Type: Package
Title: Spatiotemporal Gaussian Process Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sofia", "Vega", email = "sofia.vega@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package for simulating and fitting spatiotemporal Gaussian Process models
    with various kernel structures (separable, non-separable, ICM, Gneiting) and 
    outcome distributions (Poisson, Normal) using Stan.
